document.topic_text: Easy 1up does not have any retailable products or services, with affiliates only in a position to market Easy 1up affiliate membership itself. Once signed up, Easy 1up affiliates gift between $25 to $500 to the affiliate who also recruited them. Bundled with each gifting payment is the following: -$25 payment - MULTILEVEL MARKETING Fundamentals course and Affiliate KickStar
